summary: A cable listing identities, possibly related to Cuban matters.
summary_one_paragraph: This SECRET cable, dated December 10, 1963, originates from RECTOR and is addressed to multiple recipients with information copies to various departments including CT, CI/CPS, and FI. It lists several identities: Odon Alvarez Delala Campa, Jose Luis Gonzalez Gallarretta, Gilberto Liway Rodrigues, and Rogelio Iglesias Patino. The cable requests that the attached cable be referenced to this cable, indicating a connected or follow-up communication.
title: Listing of Identities
